Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:48.06,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,ALASAN UNTUK MEMBAWAMU KELUAR
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.52,0:23:36.96,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,GORGEOUS TIGER RELOADED
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.21,0:00:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak satu pun dari kalian yang tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.76,0:00:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa pun, sedikit pun tentangnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah cukup, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia adalah Julius.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Julius Juukulius.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.23,0:00:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian mungkin sudah bisa menebaknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.53,0:00:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia korban sang Rakus dan jadi tanpa nama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.32,0:00:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, jati dirinya tetap utuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.78,0:00:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama ini, korban sang Rakus itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.58,0:01:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti Crusch yang "ingatannya" dimakan,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.04,0:01:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}atau Rem yang "nama"\Ndan "ingatannya" dimakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.13,0:01:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, hanya "nama" Julius yang dimakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudnya dia itu pengecualian?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.30,0:01:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dilupakan orang sekitar,\Ntapi dia sendiri masih ingat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seragam itu milik kesatria.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia pasti kenal aku dan Ferris.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau mungkin lebih dekat lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.07,0:01:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setidaknya, aku menganggap kalian temanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.57,0:01:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan sekadar teman.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti ada hubungan lain, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Anastasia.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.96,0:01:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku punya usulan.\NBoleh aku utarakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekarang di kota ini ada orang-orang\Nyang wujudnya diubah sang Nafsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:01:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan mereka yang menjadi\N"tanpa nama" gara-gara sang Rakus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.31,0:02:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski kita menangkap Uskup Agung,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.56,0:02:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mereka pasti takkan mau memberi tahu\Ncara mengembalikan semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita buntu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Buat apa repot-repot memastikannya...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.61,0:02:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bagaimana kalau kita tanya\Nke orang yang benar-benar tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang yang benar-benar tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudnya yang sangat berpengetahuan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada, 'kan? Orang yang sangat\Nberpengetahuan di negeri ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak usah bertele-tele, katakan saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shaula sang Bijak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shaula?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Satu dari tiga pahlawan hebat Lugunica.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shaula sang Bijak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dulu di Kerajaan Naga Lugunica,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ada pahlawan\Nyang menorehkan prestasi besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.07,0:02:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pedang Suci dan Naga Suci.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu yang ketiga adalah sang Bijak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka disebut Tiga Pahlawan Agung.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penjaga pengetahuan yang mampu\Nmelihat segalanya di dunia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di ujung timur Kerajaan Lugunica,\Nterdapat Gurun Pasir Augria.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sana berdiri Menara Pengawas Pleiades\Nuntuk menjaga Penyihir Iri yang tersegel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.51,0:03:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika dia sang Bijak yang dimaksud,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin dia tahu jawaban yang kita cari.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terus terang, aku masih menentang ide itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tempat berbahaya yang bahkan\NReinhard pun gagal menaklukkannya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dua tahun lalu,\Nsaat anggota keluarga kerajaan jatuh sakit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dewan memerintahkanku mencari obat
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menuju Menara Pleiades.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, aku tak bisa mencapainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejauh apa pun melangkah, aku tak bisa\Nmendekati menara di kejauhan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya ada semacam penghalang.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga tak mampu menembusnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:04:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gurun Pasir Augria itu terkenal\Nsebagai sarang binatang iblis, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Natsuki dan yang lain\Nakan aman melewatinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita hanya bisa percaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tugasku adalah mengawal\NNona Felt dan Uskup Agung.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di kota ini masih banyak orang\Nyang butuh bantuan kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempat berbahaya yang bahkan\NReinhard gagal menaklukkannya, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mendengarnya saja sudah bikin putus asa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Subaru, wajahmu jadi menakutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau kau terlalu sibuk berpikir\Nsampai lupa memberiku perhatian,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:05:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}keimutan Beti akan sia-sia, tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ditinggal melamun sebentar,\NBeako jadi kelihatan jelek.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana ada!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beatrice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah waktunya tidur, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Malam ini kita tidur bersama, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.67,0:05:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bergadang tak baik buat tubuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Natsuki, masih belum tidur?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski rute ini aman,\Nlebih baik tetap ada yang berjaga, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita kurang orang, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harusnya Ricardo juga ikut kita.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayang, tangannya...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kalau kau jujur saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.05,0:06:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Ada apa tiba-tiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bicara apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hentikan sandiwara konyolmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau bukan Anastasia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.85,0:06:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bertindak seenaknya\Ndengan wajah dan suara itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aneh sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau tahu aku bukan Ana?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.48,0:06:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari tadi aku sudah merasa janggal,\Ntapi sekarang aku yakin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anastasia itu memang realistis,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.78,0:06:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi kalau orang terdekatnya cedera parah,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.66,0:06:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia takkan bicara sedingin itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau terus-terusan ketahuan,\Naku jadi tak punya muka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terus-terusan?\NAda yang tahu selain aku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Priscilla Barielle.\NDia memanggilku rubah betina.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memang menakutkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa kau ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa tujuanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Echidna.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namaku Echidna.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asal-usulku, yah...\Nbisa dibilang aku roh buatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jujur, wajar saja kalau kau\Nmengira aku merebut tubuh Ana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya aku ragu\Nmengatakan yang sebenarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.04,0:07:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lelucon macam apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau Echidna?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.79,0:07:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan tubuh Anastasia?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bilang...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keributan di Pristella itu juga ulahmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bi-Bisa tenang dulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya ada kesalahpahaman besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana aku bisa tenang?\NDasar penyihir licik!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau apakan Anastasia?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong jangan anggap aku dalangnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak berniat menyakiti Ana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah bersama Ana lebih dari 10 tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih dari 10 tahun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kuluruskan kesalahpahaman ini dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Echidna yang kau pikirkan itu\Nentitas yang berbeda denganku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:08:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain fakta bahwa aku roh buatan
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan namaku Echidna,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku tak punya ingatan apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Roh buatan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama seperti Beako?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih tepatnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}syal bulu rubah yang dikenakan\NAna inilah wujud asliku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena itu, aku selalu mengamati kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.40,0:08:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau baru mengatakannya sekarang
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena persiapanmu mengambil alih\Ntubuh Anastasia sudah matang,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Syaldna?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Syaldna"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku agak kurang nyaman dipanggil begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sama sekali tak berniat\Nmengambil alih tubuh Ana.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Situasi saat ini di luar kendaliku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau di luar kendalimu,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kenapa tak kembali jadi syal bulu rubah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga inginnya begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.84,0:08:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku tak bisa kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.64,0:08:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jelaskan padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana kondisi tubuh Anastasia sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Singkatnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}eksistensiku menimpa kesadaran Ana\Ndengan Odo miliknya sebagai perantara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.61,0:09:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kesadaran Ana tertidur dalam Odo miliknya
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan tubuhnya bisa aku gerakkan sesukaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bahkan bisa menggunakan sihir\Nkarena gerbang Ana yang cacat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gerbang yang cacat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah pakai sihir di tubuh begitu\Nakan membebani Anastasia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama tak membahayakan nyawanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak awal nyawanya memang sudah terancam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu, aku sudah membicarakannya dengan Ana\Ndan mendapat izinnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, ini bukan pertama kalinya\Nkau meminjam tubuhnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.64,0:09:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terhitung sudah beberapa kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi baru kali ini aku tak bisa kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya, aku juga bingung\Ndengan situasi ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ini... suka Ana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah perasaanku ini tepat atau tidak,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku sadar kalau\Naku menganggapnya seperti keluarga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau bisa, aku ingin dia tetap sehat
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan yang terpenting, aku ingin dia bahagia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.84,0:10:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti, alasanmu\Ningin bertemu sang Bijak...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya ingin tahu\Ncara mengembalikan tubuh Ana.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk itu, aku akan memanfaatkan kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memangnya ada jaminan kalau sang Bijak
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.61,0:10:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tahu cara mengembalikannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.20,0:10:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, kalau dia sang Bijak
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang melihat dan tahu segalanya,\Nada kemungkinannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya memilih peluang yang paling besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan berarti aku langsung menerimanya,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi untuk sekarang aku paham.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau punya tujuan yang harus dilakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:11:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu tak menghalangi tujuan kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.52,0:11:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.98,0:11:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita sama-sama punya pertanyaan\Nuntuk sang Bijak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi soal kau meminjam tubuh Anastasia,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jangan beri tahu Julius atau siapa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.74,0:11:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak keberatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aneh juga kau bilang begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cuma tak mau bikin kacau
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}di situasi yang sudah ruwet begini.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada orang lain yang ingin kau tolong\Nlewat bantuan sang Bijak, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanti kita akan mampir ke kediaman Mathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin untuk persiapan melewati gurun,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.77,0:11:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi di sana juga ada "putri tidur".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau berniat membawanya ikut, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurutku itu tak buruk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita akan selamatkan semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada akhirnya,\Ndia hanyalah salah satu dari mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keuntungan sekecil itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa tak masalah untuk kau ambil, Natsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah terima laporannya lewat surat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Katanya, saat melawan sekte penyihir,\Njumlah korban bisa ditekan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga lega Garf bisa membantu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Otto juga kabarnya tak terluka parah...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ih! Otto itu selalu memaksakan diri!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.36,0:12:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal kami lega dapat laporan bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar pertemuan dengan\Norang-orang licik itu berjalan lancar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nanti ceritakan soal itu padaku, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.66,0:12:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, bukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, ternyata Natsuki memang nakal, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Subaru, sekarang aku paham kenapa\Nkau disebut penakluk anak kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asal tahu saja,\NPetra itu bukan anak kecil lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.67,0:13:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalaupun iya, yang kuanggap\Nanak kecil itu cuma Beako!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal Pristella, bukan hanya\Nkarena usaha Garfiel dan Otto,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi semua orang di sana\Njuga ikut berjuang keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk menyelamatkan korban\NRakus dan sang Nafsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalian akan ke Menara sang Bijak?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perjalanan yang berbahaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.07,0:13:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kalian punya peluang menang?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kukira Marquis Mathers\Nakan sangat khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, saat ini di Pristella,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}masih banyak yang terluka fisik dan mental\Nakibat ulah sekte penyihir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh pemilihan kata yang elegan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak ada dalam ingatanku, itu artinya...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.97,0:13:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau juga korban, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.18,0:13:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita fokus bicara ini dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Alasan kami mampir ke sini\Nadalah soal Rem dan satu hal lagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penjara bawah tanah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal dia, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.24,0:14:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, ada tamu yang jarang terlihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ada urusan penting denganmu, Meili.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau soal Gurun Pasir Augria,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku pernah ke sana\Nuntuk menambah koleksi binatang iblis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sana isinya cuma binatang iblis, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah, itu tuh! Yang itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin dengar pendapat\Ndari orang yang berpengalaman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.80,0:14:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Informasi dari yang berpengalaman\Ndan tidak itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berbeda jauh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bikin pemula lebih percaya diri, gitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.65,0:14:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau butuh sesuatu,\Nkenapa tak bilang langsung saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.74,0:14:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau ada kau si pengguna binatang iblis,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}mungkin kami bisa melewati gurun pasir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.83,0:14:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya, apa kau mau ikut kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.54,0:14:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu kau tak ingin keluar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi cobalah... pertimbangkan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bilang, aku ayo-ayo saja ikut.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Serius?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.22,0:15:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa lakukan apa pun\Npada binatang iblis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menjauhkan, menjinakkan,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.81,0:15:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}membuat saling bunuh atau\Nmenyuruh mereka memakan sang Bijak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.85,0:15:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, jangan lakukan yang terakhir itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu, padahal sebelumnya\Nkau tak pernah mau keluar rumah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketahuan mama memang menakutkan, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku juga tak mau terkurung selamanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bukan jalan-jalan yang menyenangkan, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah lama aku tak jalan-jalan,\Nakan seru kalau menegangkan, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah! Tolong bantuannya, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan sok dekat, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berbeda dengan Petra dan Beatrice, tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa, Julius?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sedang berpikir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentang melupakan
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.99,0:16:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan dilupakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana yang lebih menyakitkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mana tahu soal itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.54,0:16:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudahlah, jangan dipikirkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.96,0:16:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melupakan atau dilupakan itu\Nsama-sama tak berguna!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak usah sok membandingkan\Nmana yang lebih menyakitkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan pasang muka lemah begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau lupa, Julius?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak. Jangan lupakan, Julius!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ini sangat tahu kekuatanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasa maluku tahu itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski semua orang melupakanmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar-benar pria yang luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jadi sadar kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu. Kau benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata aku tak tertinggal begitu saja, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan tertinggal juga, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau sudah unggul tiga kuda di depan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa selisih tiga kuda sudah cukup?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.76,0:17:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hajar juga kau!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.93,0:17:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku dan Beako sekarang\Nsudah jauh beda dari sebelumnya, lo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ram.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku habis bersiap untuk berangkat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengganti pakaian dan menyeka tubuhnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hidungmu kembang-kempis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mesum.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku diam bingung mau jawab apa,\Nmalah dibilang mesum.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kali ini kau mungkin akan mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau mau ke sana, Barusu?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin, karena aku ingin jadi orang pertama\Nyang dia lihat saat bangun nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau bicara tanpa perasaan,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sebenarnya siapa saja juga terserah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:18:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kalau aku libatkan perasaan,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku yang ingin menolongnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin menyelamatkannya sepenuh hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf aku terlambat datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Banyak masalah yang harus aku selesai...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku cuma beralasan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya, mungkin aku bisa menggapainya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan membawamu kembali, Rem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah sumpahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal kalian sudah datang ke sini,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi maaf aku tak menyiapkan apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.49,0:18:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, maaf, sudah datang tiba-tiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak bermaksud merepotkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama sekali tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Justru meluangkan waktu datang ke sini
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sudah seperti penyemangat bagi kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Anu...\N- Suamiku,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Garek akan segera kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku percaya padanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diriku yang dulunya hampa,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.31,0:19:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}diberikan 10 tahun kebahagiaan oleh Garek.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.35,0:19:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memberiku putri dan putra yang lucu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, bagaimana mungkin\Naku tak percaya pada Garek?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau benar-benar kuat, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, tentu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku ini ibu dari dua anak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya, ada satu hal\Nyang ingin kutanyakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gorgeous Tiger,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kenapa kamu sangat peduli dengan kami?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}So-Soal itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.14,0:20:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya tak bisa melepaskan\Npandanganku dari kalian.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian itu... gampang hilang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.72,0:20:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, jahatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi karena benar, aku tak bisa membantah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, gampang hilang? Rambut?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rambut Mimi juga gampang rontok kalau panas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tidak apa-apa, Gorgeous Tiger?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah kenapa
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.71,0:20:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kamu terlihat seperti anak kecil\Nyang menangis padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu, Ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.68,0:20:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku... Ibu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.07,0:20:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Garfiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.78,0:21:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namanya Garfiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Garfiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.28,0:21:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.50,0:21:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah, sudah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.37,0:21:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Garf, anak baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.35,0:21:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu anak baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.37,0:21:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu sudah berjuang keras.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.77,0:21:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.52,0:21:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selalu berjuang
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.56,0:21:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan terus berusaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi aku banyak melakukan kesalahan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.43,0:21:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski begitu, semuanya...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak apa-apa, Garf.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.33,0:21:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ibu ada di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.30,0:22:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Garf, kau tak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.30,0:22:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.93,0:22:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gorgeous Tiger, kamu baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Laki-laki kok menangis sesenggukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf sudah membuat kalian khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.17,0:22:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan pulang, jadi tak perlu khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Datanglah lagi di lain waktu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika ingin menangis,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan pinjamkan pelukanku\Nsebagai pengganti ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.23,0:22:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebisa mungkin takkan kulakukan lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, kalian berdua.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.17,0:22:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ucapkan selamat tinggal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.24,0:22:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gorgeous Tiger, sampai jumpa lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.90,0:22:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, Rafiel juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.47,0:22:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rafiel?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.70,0:22:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, Rafiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.80,0:22:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, aku belum pernah memperkenalkannya, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.07,0:22:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nama mereka berdua.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.85,0:22:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fred dan Rafiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.77,0:22:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akulah yang menamai mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.63,0:22:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau yang menamai mereka?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.23,0:22:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.40,0:23:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat memikirkan nama\Nuntuk anak-anakku yang manis,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.47,0:23:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tiba-tiba terpikirkan begitu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.69,0:23:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Fred, Rafiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Frederica, Garfiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.12,0:23:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa, Rafiel, Fred.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.63,0:23:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan datang lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.92,0:23:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, Gorgeous Tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.50,0:23:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lain kali jangan menangis lagi, lo, ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.33,0:23:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih, ibu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.07,0:23:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan mampir lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sehat-sehatlah sampai nanti.
